reviewText: By now all of you know the story so I won't comment on that. I'll remark on the 3D Blue Ray transfer. Guys, the 3D version looks phenomenal on my LG OLED TV with Passive 3D. This is one for collection and entertainment for those who love 3D Home movies

The 3D disc was fine... however, the digital copy of the movie is only good in either England or Ireland. Since I live in New Mexico, the digital copy part of the package is worthless. Therefore, I'm returning it.

This should be on every top 10 list for 3d movies.  In my opinion it was much better than 3d Avitar.  So far it is the best 3d movie that I have seen.  Bought it the day after I rented it at a local movie rental store.
Great deal on a 3D movie and the movie is very good.
It was extremely enjoyable. I very much liked the 3D format.

this is a awesome movie. they finally made another great Jurassic park film. when I heard about this one I thought it was I remake but it's not it's a continue off the other films. in this movie john Hammond gives the park to a new owner and he reopens the park and it is available to the public. but when a science project gone wrong starts terrorizing the park it's up to owen(pratt) to save the day. this movie is just as good as the first 3. I'm glad that this is not a remake. the story is good, the acting is good and the special effects is good. and this is the first time they introduce a water dinosaur. great movie hope there will be more. if you have not seen this movie then I recommend you do
Good film, bad version. 18 for a film with no extras and no 2d. Shame on you universal.
I am one of the few people who still buy 3D movies when they are available.

I've watched the movie many times in various formats but this was my first time watching a 3D movie on the PSVR.  I was pleasantly surprised.  Watching this version brought so many new details to my attention.  Give it a try and you won't regret it.

The discs are printed in French and the HD access code is not acceptable. It is for another country that the United States. I have never seen anything like this and the seller has not responded. Do not buy!!!!!
Enjoy watching 3D movies on my TV

Great 3D! The first movie i watched on my new high end 3D projector and it did not disappoint. I have watched this movie so many times so I bought the 3D version for the low cost to try out my new 3D system and it was fun to watch in 3D. The Jurassic series are among my favorites.
its awesome we got a chance to finally test out with our 3d projector !!!
Really good quality 3D and a great reboot to the series.
Great movie is even greater in 3D. Dinosaurs came to live. The disk quality was good. No freezing scenes.
